high_descs: Turn left and then left again to stand in front of the tub.
Pick the empty toilet paper roll up from the side of the tub.
Turn around and cross the room and then go right to face the toilet paper holder on the wall to the left of the toilet.
Put the empty roll on the toilet paper holder.
anns.task_desc: Put an empty toilet paper roll on a toilet paper holder.

high_descs: Turn left keeping the black door on your right and go to the sink across the room from it.
Pick up the toilet paper roll in the sink.
Turn around and go towards the black door turning right to get to the toilet.
Put the toilet paper roll on the hanger next to the toilet on the left.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the toilet paper roll and put it by the toilet.

high_descs: Turn around and go across the bathroom to the bathtub.
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll on the edge of the bathtub.
Turn back around and go to the toilet paper holder, on the wall, to the left of the toilet.
Place the empty toilet paper roll on the toilet paper holder, hanging from the wall.
anns.task_desc: Put an empty toilet paper roll on the toilet paper dispenser.
